{"tid":1034124,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有得移民， 都揀留喺香港，想睇住佢有興盛直到存亡","createTime":"2019-02-23T16:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T18:14:08.000Z","uid":233180,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e34e7de6fa8e2395d193b140f500545e6c51be77","tid":1034124,"uid":233180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:07:05.000Z","msg":"每一套戲總會有佢嘅結局，無論個結局係好係壞，睇完之後你都覺得好似了咗個心願咁。<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解有時我喺度諗如果有得揀未來移民與否&hellip;<br />\n我都想親眼睇住香港死&hellip;<br />\n相信到時好震撼&hellip;<br />\n取消一國兩制&hellip;等等&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n就好似幫你準備去睇一套戲嘅時候你上網已經睇咗劇透 知道個結局係好悲痛，但你唔會選擇唔睇(移民)，你都想睇埋佢。<br />\n<br />\n雖然移民好似唔錯但係真係會唔捨得香港同所有去香港唔識嘅人( 除非佢哋全部同我一齊移民去同一個國家， 當然啦呢個機會係冇可能<br />\n<br />\n可能將來嘅中國真係會好興盛<br />\n<br />\n但係到時嗰啲人嘅價值觀同理念同人情未完全與香港冇關，或者已經完全唔同曬，就好似你行出街你會覺得嗰度 已經 唔係你一直熟悉嘅地方<br />\n<br />\nsor for 1999 中文攞1"},{"pid":"65ac033d1cdf4f32f1a7e0a59fe73982e49e7ba7","tid":1034124,"uid":233180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2918027eb199e2d6e5a2457de9b43d4c18336b8","tid":1034124,"uid":233180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f654adca4cc26e663dec06a817b2126a81e4dc2c","tid":1034124,"uid":233180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11bffd07951815a884ddd11249c5832b76fa8bc6","tid":1034124,"uid":233180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:25:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399ad0962d3245783894401adab596ea2c804bed","tid":1034124,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:35:05.000Z","msg":"走得都唔走正on9, 去左外國唔識睇英文新聞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dab07533237c6f95aa80470827ed3a3a0b2bbe5","tid":1034124,"uid":233180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"399ad0962d3245783894401adab596ea2c804bed","tid":1034124,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:35:05.000Z","msg":"走得都唔走正on9, 去左外國唔識睇英文新聞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:40:48.000Z","msg":"咁你都會唔捨得呢度嘅人㗎嘛<br />\n<br />\n可能奴性太重太重<br />\n想親眼睇住佢死"},{"pid":"18e7ffaf826c77e39f958a752a091dd65c6d6cbc","tid":1034124,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T18:14:08.000Z","msg":"寫得好"}]}